inform_of_buy

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
inform_of_buy -  This method is called when something is bought and tells us how much has been spent.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void inform_of_buy(int value,
object * obs,
object player,
string * sellers,
string * names,
string * cats,
int * values)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^value%^RESET%^ - of the the items sold
%^BOLD%^obs%^RESET%^ - the objects bought
%^BOLD%^player%^RESET%^ - who bought them
%^BOLD%^sellers%^RESET%^ - the people whose items were bought
%^BOLD%^names%^RESET%^ - the names of the items bought
%^BOLD%^cats%^RESET%^ - the categories of the items bought
%^BOLD%^values%^RESET%^ - the values of each item

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/shops/inherit/craft_shop.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method is called when something is bought and tells us how much
has been spent.
